Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.42,0:03:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\be8\bord2\an3\fad(1000,600)\3c&HFFFFFF&\t(0,1000,1,\3c&H000000&)\pos(1171,600)}—不变的孩子—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是偶然的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:52.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是经由他人抱着某种目的而制造出来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.56,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(774,660)}Killing Goods
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然同被称为杀害遗品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:04:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其诞生方式以及性质又与一般事物截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.47,0:04:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是“定制品”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋装没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刀也带齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备完毕 爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蜜莉会加油报仇的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.66,0:04:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.84,0:04:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了小切 今天能…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正要出门 能改天再说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.00,0:04:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\an7}早安！ \N现在就去帮你剪头发 \N之后要去哪里玩吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.01,0:04:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35}对不起 \N今天有要事要办 \N明天再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明好想见小切的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.58,0:05:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他来了也只会失望罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.73,0:05:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么头发没变长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还是剪不断
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.37,0:05:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能想到的可能性只有昨天的晚会
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但到底是为什么呢
